      "text": [
        "4136 - وَ رُوِيَ : \"أَنَّهُ إِنْ خَرَقَ أُكِلَ وَ إِنْ لَمْ يَخْرِقْ لَمْ يُؤْكَلْ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4136 - And it was narrated:\n\"If it pierced, it may be eaten, but if it did not pierce, it may not be eaten.\""
        ]
      }
